  npcName: Android 278 Visual Recording
  npcPortrait: {fileID: -7527145504033472756, guid: bb42bd1a868c3c245843349a9ded47ee, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - 'Backup Recording of Human Retrieval. Recovering now.  '
  - '[Android 278 is seen to be looking at their superior.] '
  - '[Presumably their creator.] '
  - Android 278, Android 279, and Android 280. Tasked to scan the disaster area of
    the Northern to Western area.
  - And if any human is discovered. Retrieve their body if proved to be unconscious.
  - 'Aid their injuries when proved to be alive. '
  - 'Understood? '
  - 'Mission accepted.  '
  - '[Footage is disrupted. Androids are seen walking away onto a tunnel.]  '
